    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering linear power through six individual throttle bodies and high-pressure double VANOS variable valve timing. The Getrag 420G 6-speed manual gearbox provides precise engagement, paired with a factory M Variable Differential Lock for optimal torque vectoring. Recent maintenance includes a comprehensive subframe reinforcement and a valve adjustment to ensure the high-revving valvetrain remains within spec. Suspended on a balanced MacPherson strut front and multi-link rear setup, this chassis offers telepathic feedback. While showing honest wear consistent with its enthusiast-driven history, the mechanical vitals remain robust and the compression across all six cylinders is excellent.",
