      "description": "This vehicle has been a reliable companion, meticulously maintained and kept in a climate-controlled garage. The exterior retains a deep, lustrous finish, with only the slightest imperfections expected from a car that has enjoyed the open road. Inside, the cabin remains a sanctuary of comfort; the upholstery is supple and free of tears, while every button, dial, and digital display functions exactly as it did the day it rolled off the lot. Mechanically, it is in excellent health, benefiting from a rigorous service schedule\u2014recent oil changes, brake inspections, and a new set of premium tires ensure it is ready for its next owner immediately. Whether you're commuting or taking a weekend getaway, this car offers a smooth, quiet, and confident ride. It is a complete package for someone seeking a premium experience without the new-car price tag.",
      "price": 34500.0,
